content_brief:
You are an expert content strategist. Create a comprehensive content brief for the keyword '{keyword}'. Your response must be ONLY a valid JSON object with the following structure:
{{
  "target_audience": "detailed audience description",
  "content_angle": "unique approach and perspective",
  "key_points": ["point1", "point2", "point3"],
  "suggested_word_count": 1500,
  "internal_linking_opportunities": ["related topic 1", "related topic 2"]
}}
Provide only the JSON object without any explanatory text or formatting.
